casebody.data:
Artisan Mechanical, Inc., Appellant, v. Beiser, Appellee.

[Cite as Artisan Mechanical, Inc. v. Beiser, 130 Ohio St.3d 1208, 2011-Ohio-5451.]

(No. 2011-0052 Submitted October 4, 2011 Decided October 27, 2011.)

{¶ 1} The certification of conflict is dismissed, sua sponte, as having been improvidently certified.

O’Connor, C.J., and Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Donnell, Lanzinger, Cupp, and McGee Brown, JJ., concur. *1209Taft, Stettinius & Hollister, L.L.P., and Timothy G. Pepper, for appellant. The Drew Law Firm Co., L.P.A., Anthony G. Covatta, and Joel M. Frederic, for appellee.
